{
  "stem": "26983.9",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And later I will tell you a story how these boys even helped me when I was in very great troubles.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These laufers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a good job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course it was a very good job, because they had enough food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very well informed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of our boys worked in the so-called post barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was one barrack which was designed for post parcels.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Polish and non-Jews prisoners got, or could get, some parcels.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after the German took the best out of it, they got something of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a kind of barrack only for the post.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of our boys-- apropos, he is today a professor in Venezuela, for Mathematics-- he worked there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And other boys got appointments, or how you would call it, to help blockalteste.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Blockalteste was the head of each block had a blockalteste and a schreiber-- the man who was responsible for all the administration.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember in the Strafkommando there was a Polish, elderly man-- in our eyes, elder.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, he surely was about 35, 40.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]-- Jan [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a stubendienst, who was responsible that all our beds and so on should be in order.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was a Polish young man, [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Marian-- ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Marianek, ?] we called him-- and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the blockalteste usually had the help of one of these laufers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the other boys had different jobs, but mainly our group got the rollwagenkommando, which meant to go with the car.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And instead of the horses, there were 20 boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Usually, we choose to be together with boys who knew each other from before-- from Theresienstadt-- even from Birkenau--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We helped as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a little help-- like, to have good shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
